      <h3 class="margin">好物推荐</h3><br>

      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p>景德镇陶瓷匠人手作，温润细腻</p>
            <img src="http://oqym24k6p.bkt.clouddn.com/xiaoyi/2017-06-03-IMG_4752.JPG" class="img-responsive margin" style="width:100%" alt="Image">
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p>百年老树普洱茶饼</p>
            <img src="http://oqym24k6p.bkt.clouddn.com/xiaoyi/2017-06-03-IMG_4751.JPG" class="img-responsive margin" style="width:100%" alt="Image">
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p>四遍摇清“神火”焙火</p>
            <img src="http://oqym24k6p.bkt.clouddn.com/xiaoyi/2017-06-03-IMG_4753.JPG" class="img-responsive margin" style="width:100%" alt="Image">
          </div>
      </div>
</div>



